{
  "stem": "27390.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We heard something's going on outside, shouting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he looked and saw soldiers running around with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they didn't know whether they were German soldiers or Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a lot of shooting going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "After about a half hour it died down, the shooting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And somebody shouted, the Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we all got up, and it was all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went out into the street, and we saw the Russian tanks coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we jumped onto the tanks, and we drove in-- it was already getting daylight in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we drove into a little town there called [INAUDIBLE], which was not very far from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we came into this town on the Russian tanks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I must say the Russians were very good to us at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they said, you can do what you like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And you went into the- there were a lot of German shops there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So we started raiding these German shops.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I got hold of-- we children-- I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I didn't have the adults looked for jewelry, valuables, what to get hold of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were only interested in one thing, food, and food, and food only.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we- I got-- we- we managed to get, uh, break into a shop that was selling all kinds of tinned in jars conserves, apples, pears, blackberries.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got hold of a box of blackberry jars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I run out into the street with this box of blackberry jars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got hold of a German girl passed with a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I told her to get off the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I put this box on the back of the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how I drove back into the ghetto with the jars of blackberries.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
